OL,7,FSir Mel Stride will seek to restore
OL,8,Fthe Conservative Party's reputation
OL,9,Ffor economic responsibility as he sets
OL,10,Fout plans to slash #47 billion of
OL,11,FGovernment spending.
OL,13,FThe shadow chancellor is expected to
OL,14,Fuse his speech to the Tory conference
OL,15,Fin Manchester on Monday to set out a
OL,16,Fplan to cut welfare spending, foreign
OL,17,Faid and the Civil Service if his party
OL,18,Fwins the next election.
